This is a jail map that I made for [BHP] 

This map includes

Room for 12 T's and 8 CT's
Pool area for free day
Shot 4 Shot and gun toss areas for Last Request
Big Cage
Infirmary
Solitary
Armory
Towers around the four sides of the map for snipers
Many secrets

O is for Open C is for Close in case you can't figure that out
